Package: railwayJP
Title: Plot Japanese Railway Routes Using Government Open Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Soichiro", "Yamauchi", email = "soichiro@alumni.princeton.edu", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Plot railway routes across Japan using the National Land Numerical
    Information (Kokudo Suuchi Jouhou) railway dataset from the Ministry of Land,
    Infrastructure, Transport and Tourism (MLIT). Features include graph-based
    routing between stations, support for specifying intermediate stops (via points),
    automatic operator corporate colors, and customizable map output.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
